subject: CNC machining for carbon fiber and aluminum products
description_text:
Hi friend,
I’m Jack, the manager at iKabon. I came across your website and was impressed by your company’s reputation. I notice that your company sell some carbon fiber parts and aluminum parts.
At iKabon, we specialize in high-precision CNC machining for carbon fiber and aluminum products. With fast lead times, strict tolerance control, and competitive price, we help our clients improve efficiency and reduce costs.
If you're looking to optimize your supply chain or looking for a reliable/long-term business manufacturing partner, I’d love to connect further and see how we can support your business.
Looking forward to hearing from you.
Best regards,
Jack Tsang
Manager, iKabon
